# tpd/

Technical Product Design documentation for Intent v2.1.0, organized as a comprehensive reference guide covering system architecture, requirements, implementation strategy, and operational guidelines. This directory contains the complete as-built specification for the Intent system (formerly STP).

## Files

- `technical_product_design.md` -- Main TPD index and entry point with agent system overview
- `1_introduction.md` -- Purpose, scope, system overview, and version history of Intent
- `2_requirements.md` -- Functional and non-functional requirements with implementation status
- `3_architecture.md` -- System architecture overview, component design, and data flow
- `4_detailed_design.md` -- Directory structure, templates, configuration system, and JSON schema
- `5_implementation_strategy.md` -- Development approach, steel thread breakdown, and task organization
- `6_deployment_and_operations.md` -- Installation methods, project initialization, and operational procedures
- `7_technical_challenges_and_mitigations.md` -- LLM context management, portability, and adoption strategies
- `8_appendices.md` -- Glossary, command reference, configuration schema, and examples
